Menlyn is Pretoria's fastest-growing commercial district, anchored by Menlyn Maine and Menlyn Park Shopping Centre. The node hosts regional head offices, financial services firms and a dense cluster of conferencing venues, making it a first choice for consultants and project teams working east of the capital.
